Privacy Policy for NextLevel Game

Effective Date: [Insert Date]

This Privacy Policy describes how NextLevel Game ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and discloses your Personal Information when you use our [Game Name] application ("Application") available on Google Play Store.

1. Information Collection

We collect the following types of information when you use our Application:

Personal Information: This includes your name, email address, and any other details you provide in your user profile.
Device Information: We collect information specific to the device you use, such as the model, operating system, and IP address.
Usage Data: Information on how you use the Application, such as your game progress, levels achieved, and interactions with game features.
2. How We Use Your Information

We use the information we collect to:

Provide, maintain, and improve our Application.
Communicate with you, including providing customer support and updates about the Application.
Personalize your game experience.
Conduct analytics to understand how our users interact with our Application.
3. Information Sharing

We may share your information with third parties in the following circumstances:

Service Providers: We may share your information with companies that provide services on our behalf, such as data analysis and customer service.
Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information if required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities.
Business Transfers: In the event of a merger, acquisition, or asset sale, your Personal Information may be transferred.
4. Security

We take reasonable measures to protect your Personal Information from loss, theft, misuse, and unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction.

5. International Transfers

Your information may be transferred to — and maintained on — computers located outside of your state, province, country, or other governmental jurisdiction where the privacy laws may not be as protective as those in your jurisdiction.

6. Your Privacy Rights

You have the right to access, update, or to delete the Personal Information we collect on you. You can do this by using the settings within our Application or contacting us directly.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

Email: support@nextlevelgame.com
